        Facebook Android resources are now injected from build config.
        1. Go to https://developers.facebook.com/apps and create or open your app.
        2. Copy the Facebook App ID and Client Token into either:
           - environment variables FACEBOOK_APP_ID and FACEBOOK_CLIENT_TOKEN, or
           - entries with those names in local.properties.
        3. Also add YOUR_PACKAGE_NAME to "Android" platform in Facebook App settings,
           and add your debug/release key hash (run the keytool command shown in the
           flutter_facebook_auth docs to get your hash).
